What you did was send a request to change some of the code in the Bitcoin Core repository, the software package that runs most of Bitcoin's network infrastructure.

If you just want to buy bitcoins, you need to sign up for some exchange and/or find someone who wants to sell them to you. Search a bit on the internet. This is not the right place.

Okay thank you
